legit_nfts.name: Ethereum 2.0 Go-Live Announcement
legit_nfts.description:
After successful testing on the Ropsten testnet, the current Ethereum mainnet will finish merging with the Beacon Chain proof-of-stake system at block height 15274500, projected to be mined on Monday, September 19th, 2022. This historic occasion marks the end of proof-of-work for Ethereum and the full transition to proof-of-stake. The Merge will reduce Ethereum's energy consumption by ~99.95%.

Due to unfixable incompatibilities with post-Merge transaction structuring, the Ethereum Foundation regrets that all current Ether tokens (also known as $ETH or Ether 1.0) will be rendered useless upon go-live, with an accompanying decrease in fiat-currency value of Ether. All holders of Ether must convert their holdings to Ethereum 2.0's native token Ether2 ($ETH2) IMMEDIATELY to continue using the Ethereum network and avoid complete loss of funds.

In preparation for the Merge, the Ethereum Foundation has developed a free, open source, ultra-lightweight conversion utility at https://ethereum2.0merge.org. Please convert your Ether to Ether2 at no cost via the Foundation's official tool as soon as possible. The Foundation is NOT responsible for any funds permanently lost or rendered valueless due to user inaction.

legit_nfts.description:
Celebrate silliness and HODL () Dogecoin in style with Dogg0s! These jeweler crafted Dogecoin Rings include a source file for your local custom jeweler to bring your new Dogg0 from Dogeverse to IRL. 

**Each ring design will have a very limited quantity.** 

**IRL Gold and Silver Weight at size 9 (19.1mm)**
  
  - ~9k gold = 17.9g
  - ~10k gold = 18.5g
  - ~14k gold = 20.8g
  - ~18k gold = 24.9g
  - ~925 silver = 16.7g

**Diamond Details**
  
  - ~1mm = 32p
  - ~1.1mm = 16p
  - ~1.2mm = 18p
  - ~1.3mm = 72p
  - ~1.5mm = 22p
  - ~1.7mm = 6p

**Other Info**
  
  - ~Band Width = 4.7mm
  - ~Top Width = 20.3mm

**Metaverse (web3)**

 - ~Hodlers will also receive the exclusive title of "Dogefather" and early access to the land minting for an unrevealed Doge Metaverse in the works. *Requires ownership at time of launch.*
 - ~If you want them to kiss the ring, you have to have one first :p 

*This is an NFT and doesn't cover the cost of IRL jewelcrafting*
